=== SQL QUERY EXECUTED ===
```sql
SELECT 
    c.company_name, 
    COUNT(a.invoice_id) AS pending_invoices, 
    SUM(a.balance_amount) AS total_due_payment
FROM 
    accounts a
JOIN 
    company c ON a.invoice_to_company = c.id
WHERE 
    a.status = 'unpaid' OR a.status = 'overdue'
GROUP BY 
    c.company_name
ORDER BY 
    total_due_payment DESC
```

